89 void QtDcmFindCallback::callback ( T_DIMSE_C_FindRQ *request, int responseCount, T_DIMSE_C_FindRSP *rsp, DcmDataset *responseIdentifiers )
90 {
91  QMap<QString, QString> infosMap;
92 
93  OFString info;
94 
95  switch ( d->type )
96  {
97 
98  case QtDcmFindCallback::PATIENT:
99  responseIdentifiers->findAndGetOFString ( DCM_PatientName, info );
100  infosMap.insert ( "Name", QString ( info.c_str() ) );
101  responseIdentifiers->findAndGetOFString ( DCM_PatientID, info );
102  infosMap.insert ( "ID", QString ( info.c_str() ) );
103  responseIdentifiers->findAndGetOFString ( DCM_PatientSex, info );
104  infosMap.insert ( "Sex", QString ( info.c_str() ) );
105  responseIdentifiers->findAndGetOFString ( DCM_PatientBirthDate, info );
106  infosMap.insert ( "Birthdate", QString ( info.c_str() ) );
107 
108  QtDcmManager::instance()->foundPatient ( infosMap );
109 
110  break;
111 
112  case QtDcmFindCallback::STUDY:
113  responseIdentifiers->findAndGetOFString ( DCM_StudyDescription, info );
114  infosMap.insert ( "Description", QString ( info.c_str() ) );
115  responseIdentifiers->findAndGetOFString ( DCM_StudyDate, info );
116  infosMap.insert ( "Date", QString ( info.c_str() ) );
117  responseIdentifiers->findAndGetOFString ( DCM_StudyID, info );
118  infosMap.insert ( "ID", QString ( info.c_str() ) );
119  responseIdentifiers->findAndGetOFString ( DCM_StudyInstanceUID, info );
120  infosMap.insert ( "UID", QString ( info.c_str() ) );
121 
122  QtDcmManager::instance()->foundStudy ( infosMap );
123 
124  break;
125 
126  case QtDcmFindCallback::SERIE:
127  responseIdentifiers->findAndGetOFString ( DCM_SeriesDescription, info );
128  infosMap.insert ( "Description", QString ( info.c_str() ) );
129  responseIdentifiers->findAndGetOFString ( DCM_StudyDate, info );
130  infosMap.insert ( "Date", QString ( info.c_str() ) );
131  responseIdentifiers->findAndGetOFString ( DCM_Modality, info );
132  infosMap.insert ( "Modality", QString ( info.c_str() ) );
133  responseIdentifiers->findAndGetOFString ( DCM_SeriesInstanceUID, info );
134  infosMap.insert ( "ID", QString ( info.c_str() ) );
135  responseIdentifiers->findAndGetOFString ( DCM_InstitutionName, info );
136  infosMap.insert ( "Institution", QString ( info.c_str() ) );
137  responseIdentifiers->findAndGetOFString ( DCM_PerformingPhysicianName, info );
138  infosMap.insert ( "Operator", QString ( info.c_str() ) );
139  responseIdentifiers->findAndGetOFString ( DCM_NumberOfSeriesRelatedInstances, info );
140  infosMap.insert ( "InstanceCount", QString ( info.c_str() ) );
141 
142  QtDcmManager::instance()->foundSerie ( infosMap );
143  break;
144 
145  case QtDcmFindCallback::IMAGE:
146  responseIdentifiers->findAndGetOFString ( DCM_SOPInstanceUID, info );
147 
148 // QtDcmManager::instance()->setPreviewImageUID ( QString ( info.c_str() ) );
149  break;
150 
151  case QtDcmFindCallback::IMAGES:
152  OFString number;
153  responseIdentifiers->findAndGetOFString ( DCM_SOPInstanceUID, info );
154  responseIdentifiers->findAndGetOFString ( DCM_InstanceNumber, number );
155 
156  if ( !number.length() )
157  number = "0";
158 
159  QtDcmManager::instance()->foundImage ( QString ( info.c_str() ), QString ( number.c_str() ).toInt() );
160 
161 // responseIdentifiers->print ( std::cout );
162 
163  break;
164 
165  }
166 }
